  <figure class="container-prose post-hero">
    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-10-2025-11_41_21-PM.png" alt="Landlord Insurance for Rental Property: Don't Learn This Lesson the Hard Way" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
